source.name: Luxury Limousine Services - Vehicles
source.description: Luxury Limousine Bases provide pre-arranged premium transportation to clients throughout New York City. This list includes license numbers, names(s) of licensees, addresses, phones, and license types. This list includes detailed vehicle information, including affiliated base, license numbers, names(s) of licensees, DMV license plate and VIN numbers, license types, expiration date, and model year.
